TITLE: Using Recipe Variants as JSX Props
DESCRIPTION: Example of using recipe variants as JSX props to change component styles with proper type safety.
SOURCE: https://github.com/chakra-ui/panda/blob/main/website/pages/docs/concepts/style-props.mdx#2025-04-18_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
import { styled } from '../styled-system/jsx'
import { button, type ButtonVariantProps } from '../styled-system/recipes'

const Button = (props: ButtonVariantProps) => (
  <button className={button(props)}>Button</button>
)

const App = () => <Button variant="secondary">Button</Button>
```

