TITLE: Generated Atomic CSS by Panda
DESCRIPTION: Shows the resulting CSS generated by Panda at build time, demonstrating how atomic styles are created within the @layer utilities.
SOURCE: https://github.com/chakra-ui/panda/blob/main/website/pages/docs/concepts/writing-styles.md#2025-04-18_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: css
CODE:
```
@layer utilities {
  .bg_gainsboro {
    background-color: gainsboro;
  }

  .rounded_9999px {
    border-radius: 9999px;
  }

  .fs_13px {
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .p_10px_15px {
    padding: 10px 15px;
  }
}
```

