TITLE: Using Container Pattern with Function Syntax
DESCRIPTION: The Container pattern creates a container with max-width and centered content. This example demonstrates the function approach to create a container with default properties.
SOURCE: https://github.com/chakra-ui/panda/blob/main/website/pages/docs/concepts/patterns.mdx#2025-04-18_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
import { container } from '../styled-system/patterns'

function App() {
  return (
    <div className={container()}>
      <div>First</div>
      <div>Second</div>
      <div>Third</div>
    </div>
  )
}
```

