TITLE: Implementing Array Syntax for Responsive Styles in Panda CSS (JSX)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates the array syntax for responsive styles in Panda CSS. Each position in the array corresponds to a breakpoint, with undefined values representing breakpoints where no specific style is applied.
SOURCE: https://github.com/chakra-ui/panda/blob/main/website/pages/docs/concepts/responsive-design.md#2025-04-18_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
