TITLE: Configuring Panda CSS for Next.js App Router
DESCRIPTION: Panda CSS configuration file content for a Next.js project using App Router, specifying include paths and output directory.
SOURCE: https://github.com/chakra-ui/panda/blob/main/website/pages/docs/installation/nextjs.mdx#2025-04-18_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import { defineConfig } from "@pandacss/dev"

export default defineConfig({
  // Whether to use css reset
  preflight: true,

  // Where to look for your css declarations
  include: ["./src/components/**/*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx}", "./src/app/**/*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx}"],

  // Files to exclude
  exclude: [],

  // The output directory for your css system
  outdir: "styled-system",
})
```

