TITLE: Using Panda CSS in React Components
DESCRIPTION: JSX example demonstrating how to use Panda's utility functions and patterns for styling React components, including horizontal stacks and CSS utility styles.
SOURCE: https://github.com/chakra-ui/panda/blob/main/README.md#2025-04-18_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: jsx
