TITLE: Customizing Spacing Tokens in Panda CSS (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: This code example demonstrates how to add custom spacing tokens to the Panda CSS theme. It adds a 'gutter' spacing token with a value of '32px' in the panda.config.ts configuration file.
SOURCE: https://github.com/chakra-ui/panda/blob/main/website/pages/docs/customization/theme.mdx#2025-04-18_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { defineConfig } from '@pandacss/dev'

export default defineConfig({
  theme: {
    extend: {
      tokens: {
        spacing: {
          gutter: { value: '32px' }
        }
      }
    }
  }
})
```

