TITLE: Implementing Float Pattern in React with TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates usage of float pattern for positioning elements relative to their container using both function and JSX approaches. Requires a parent element with relative positioning.
SOURCE: https://github.com/chakra-ui/panda/blob/main/website/pages/docs/concepts/patterns.mdx#2025-04-18_snippet_19

