TITLE: Pattern Integration Example with HStack
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to integrate Panda UI patterns with style merging using the hstack pattern.
SOURCE: https://github.com/chakra-ui/panda/blob/main/website/pages/docs/concepts/writing-styles.md#2025-04-18_snippet_14

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
import { hstack } from '../styled-system/patterns'
import { css } from '../styled-system/css'

export const Button = ({ css: cssProp = {}, children }) => {
  const hstackProps = hstack.raw({
    border: '1px solid',
    _hover: { color: 'blue.400' }
  })

  const className = css(hstackProps, cssProp)

  return <button className={className}>{children}</button>
}
```

