TITLE: Token Management and Retrieval in Panda CSS
DESCRIPTION: Defines a token structure and functions to retrieve token values and CSS variables. This provides a way to access design tokens programmatically.
SOURCE: https://github.com/chakra-ui/panda/blob/main/packages/node/README.md#2025-04-18_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const tokens = {
  'colors.red.400': { value: '...', variable: '...' },
}

const tokenMap = {
  colors: [{ group: 'red', key: 'red.400', value: '...' }],
  fonts: [],
}

function getToken(path) {
  const { value } = tokens[path] || {}
  return value
}

function getTokenVar(path) {
  const { variable } = tokens[path] || {}
  return variable
}
```

