TITLE: Custom Utility with Color-mix Transform Function
DESCRIPTION: Example of creating a custom utility that uses the provided colorMix function from the utils object to transform color values with opacity.
SOURCE: https://github.com/chakra-ui/panda/blob/main/packages/core/CHANGELOG.md#2025-04-18_snippet_83

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
export default defineConfig({
  utilities: {
    background: {
      shorthand: 'bg',
      className: 'bg',
      values: 'colors',
      transform(value, args) {
        const mix = args.utils.colorMix(value)
        // This can happen if the value format is invalid (e.g. `bg: red.300/invalid` or `bg: red.300//10`)
        if (mix.invalid) return { background: value }

        return {
          background: mix.value,
        }
      },
    },
  },
})
```

